\af31506 \ltrch\fcs0 \f31506\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7733306\charrsid12002340 KnotBraid is a suite dedicated to preparing, correcting, and executing knots and braids.
\par It combines three complementary tools: KnotBraid, LogiBraiding, and LogiKnotting.
\par 
\par Home page, general overview of the suite.
\par 
\par Tip
\par To build a clean ABoK library, work first in an .lkw file, correct the crossings, check the print preview, then validate to an .lkv file only when the model is final.
\par 
\par File types
\par file.lkw: working file, editable.
\par file.lkv: validated file, locked read-only.
\par JSON: LogiBraiding braid catalog.
\par 
\par Warning
\par An .lkv file is no longer editable. To continue working from a validated model, first use the Copy command.
\par 
